lead_paragraph: Jaysean Paige scored 18 of his 25 points after halftime, Tarik Phillip connected on a floater with 4.5 seconds left in the second overtime and West Virginia toughed out an 87-83 victory over Kansas State on Saturday in the Big 12 opener for both teams.

headline.print_headline: No. 19 West Virginia Fights Off Kansas State 87-83 in 2OT
